title: $FEVR Price Prediction?
body:
Hey gang. Today will be a fun day.

We've decided to award winners of the below poll a small sum of $FEVR, enough to cover 1 basic pack.

Do you feel lucky, punk? If so, try to guess correctly how long until the RealFevr packs are sold-out. Seconds? Minutes? Hours? One day?

So many choices. Who wins?

BONUS: if you vote in the first 13 choices and win, you get an extra booster!
author: 0x985A27EC406539F569362D9D5D3681D3A08b5f72
